    840268,"Lo There Shall Come A Menace!!", 729520,"Spider-Man and Jackpot go after Menace who has just kidnapped Councilwoman Parfrey. Spider-Man manages to free her into the hands of Jackpot. Jackpot then comes back to aide Spider-Man she manages to get Menace off his glider but in the process causes the glider to crash into the Councilwoman. Jackpot is devastated and pushes Spider-Man away. Later he visits the home of Sara Ehret who he believed was Jackpot. However Sara looks different to Jackpot and initially denies any knowledge but gives him a critic answer.",NULL,"For some reason \"Editor\" is in quotes for Stephen Wacker; Dan Buckley (Original Publisher); Gale Guggenheim Slott Wells (Spidey's Braintrust); Jason Keith (Original Cover Colours)",19);
