    840271,"The Menace Of... Menace", 729520,"Spider-Man finds himself cornered by the Blue Shield but manages to get away when the Menace turns up. The Menace shocks him as a warning not to interfere with his plans. Jonah is still in hospital and his wife is hiding the fact that she has sold the paper. Whilst investigating the recent body found with a Spider-Tracer Spider-Man visits the leading Detective on the case. There he discovers that more bodies have been found with tracers on them. An explosion goes off in the distance but as Spider-Man goes to leave SHIELD turns up.",NULL,"Dan Buckley (Original Publisher); Gale Guggenheim Slott Wells (Spidey's Braintrust)",19);
