    840790,"The Dead Lover Returns!", 224740,"Ted Femur dies in a boating accident but pleads with the \"high court of the dead\" to return to the world of the living to look for the love of his life. He finds the girl who was meant for him. She doesn't see him as a rotting corpse and is willing to even marry him. But there's a catch...",NULL,"Art identification by Jim Vadeboncoeur Jr.",19);
